fields.descriptive_line: Album with textile samples and fashion plates, compiled by Barbara Johnson, England, 1746-1823.
fields.physical_description: Album consisting of ninety-seven pages of paper with textile samples and fashion plates attached. The album has a green parchment binding and more than half of the pages are blank. The samples and fashion plates are usually companied by descriptive notes.
fields.dimensions: Height: 15 in, Width: 9.75 in, Depth: 2 - 3.25 in spine, Weight: 10.62 kg
